{"tid":1908103,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"朱凱迪：隔離中心冇招標　市價估計約3,500萬 政府俾5,500萬 中資食水特深？！","createTime":"2020-03-03T04:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T06:53:42.000Z","uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"964a7e57fb445f97c16d2051924c0d81b6cdbbae","tid":1908103,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:56:35.000Z","msg":"政府直接委聘承建商建隔離中心的情況愈揭愈多，到 2 月 28 日食衛局才透過新聞稿公布，至今總共動用 3.4 億港元做 750 個單位，涉及鯉魚門、竹篙灣、西貢和八鄉四處。每單位平均價格為45萬，到底屬平定貴？綜合工程業界消息，鯉魚門和竹篙灣兩項由中資公司負責的工程，造價跟市價有距離，食水甚深。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯⋯消息指，就算加上1000萬港元平整工程，和1000萬港元工人薪水，總計也是3500萬元，不明白為何政府要支付中國建築5500萬元？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/隔離中心冇招標-中資食水特別深/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%86%87%E6%8B%9B%E6%A8%99-%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E9%A3%9F%E6%B0%B4%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%B7%B1%2F&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=3c59eeea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%86%87%E6%8B%9B%E6%A8%99-%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E9%A3%9F%E6%B0%B4%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%B7%B1%2F&h=3618f6f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/隔離中心冇招標-中資食水特別深/</a>"},{"pid":"3c5d18199c319be5007733e36c354851f8909b32","tid":1908103,"uid":123738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:13:07.000Z","msg":"依家支那無錢呀，仲唔比多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2abe8b4d62fd8a9fa1a637a6fba204b7cea89f5","tid":1908103,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:21:12.000Z","msg":"大家做生意都係求打和"},{"pid":"25bbeed8ba6bac827dc30e7119afb73ae8af4c11","tid":1908103,"uid":158235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5413ef69bd710af99bbdbf3d5868f874b76f69b","tid":1908103,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:25:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"47b522f0621f97d153647a45c996f267c18623d7","tid":1908103,"uid":442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:28:36.000Z","msg":"用撚完做隔離營肯定做集中營<br />\n今舖點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76122dddf3037d2378512eb8cb1c399d1ee42bac","tid":1908103,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:29:13.000Z","msg":"有2千萬係用黎疏通關係 (好似係)"},{"pid":"b311f28d8d406cb8db65e1077adcbe8a0bece0e5","tid":1908103,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:30:34.000Z","msg":"口罩就 價低者得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561d530538f8066c168b27cdaaa4f703caa9bcf5","tid":1908103,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:31:16.000Z","msg":"只係用多咗2千萬，今次有進步啦喎，平時最少要作到條數係8千萬..."},{"pid":"3345a92cfc4395a13aeb21af9d68bf85f7f545cb","tid":1908103,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:53:35.000Z","msg":"政府明益承建商，回歸後已成常態<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啟德體育園是首次設立「提案誘因」做法的港府工務工程，政府建議，每名落標者最多可獲6000萬元，或擬備標書所花費實際費用的一半金額。局方回應有議員早前提出，能否考慮先採用傳統方式招標，局方今午在最新文件表示，經詳細研究後，認為做法實際上不可行，因為若待未能成功吸引足夠標書，才提供「提案誘因」，有興趣參與投票的集團，均不會在採取傳統招標的第一輪入標，而會待流標後，才在提供「提案誘因」的第二輪入標，浪費時間，並令體育園造價增加。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSubmit tender已有錢分，點解政府唔先將啲錢做好周圍嘅配套，令幅地可生金，增加發展嘅回報，而係要&quot;倒貼&quot;去吸引人去開荒呢?"},{"pid":"90071120283f849ee0e55dbb4d416d0062850708","tid":1908103,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:53:42.000Z","msg":"呢D其實唔叫食水深, 係利益輸送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}